{"tid":1404134,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我呼籲全體醫護幫義士爭取休息時間","createTime":"2019-08-04T02:52:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T04:45:12.000Z","uid":109605,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"249cc4ceda3ffb2e68b2c485fb2d261b5ffb32aa","tid":1404134,"uid":109605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:52:56.000Z","msg":"尋晚俾人捉左個d，有d送左過海睇醫生。<br />\n加埋中間會有狗隻求診就醫。<br />\n作為一個專業醫護雖然罷唔到工，我呼籲大家按章工作。<br />\n<br />\n遇上被捕人士時，不要同時處理多名病人，盡量按章工作，處理前後做足洗手5步曲，三核五對，盡現我地既patient care! 最緊要係咩幫佢<span style=\"font-size: large;\">爭取休息時間</span> 加上好多被捕義士係無律師電話，星火電話 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">9819 0979</span></span><br />\n你可以係耳邊細細聲同佢講有咩症狀係唔適宜岀院，例如心口痛，抽筋。<br />\n<br />\n遇上狗隻求診時，先口述核對一次身分證號碼，隨即話聽唔到再講，三再有權要求出示身分證核對清楚  （叫狗攞id岀黎 ，呢點只有醫護人院可以做到 請各位珍惜機會) <br />\n<br />\n當狗隻想問你借凳坐時，你可以有權拒絕佢要求，我地做醫護都係坐，憑咩你有得坐<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"a7583aaf71589ae0f62dd0f6a9c51aff5057640f","tid":1404134,"uid":109605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:53:22.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"5edbe9ccb88d51b92d7b4f2dc44d6da2f3b21c44","tid":1404134,"uid":109605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:53:32.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"2bd2b8c26eac690827925115106a7f6dad534c12","tid":1404134,"uid":109605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:53:42.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"5665560dfddda64999b616fe1ab302e59138ec3a","tid":1404134,"uid":109605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:53:52.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"d7397ddc4ab003faeb66b8fb9354b2309d6d51c2","tid":1404134,"uid":109605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:54:03.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"694a5e8201c7b9d12b99e91822a6369418a6ce48","tid":1404134,"uid":109605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:54:15.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"5df61103e870a9f054db703cd1ac464de604236e","tid":1404134,"uid":109605,"li